     │ 📊 Scientific Validation                                                                                                                             │
     │                                                                                                                                                      │
     │ 1. Domain Accuracy: Each package maps to fundamental science                                                                                         │
     │ 2. Literature Alignment: Connects to existing 345-paper database                                                                                     │
     │ 3. Performance Validation: Predictions testable against literature                                                                                   │
     │ 4. Material Coverage: Complete electrode material spectrum                                                                                           │
     │ 5. Application Relevance: Real-world system design capabilities                                                                                      │
     │                                                                                                                                                      │
     │ This comprehensive architecture transforms MESSAi into a true scientific composition platform where researchers can systematically explore the       │
     │ complete design space of bioelectrochemical systems, from low-cost copper cathodes to high-performance platinum systems.             